ecific knowledge in\nthe top layers of the BERT, whereas the benefit from the pre-trained BERT model\nis from the bottom layers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 17:43:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-26"}
