semi-analytically. The analytic\nand semi-analytic microlensing solutions associated with this work may allow\nfor substantially faster light-curve calculations and modeling of observed\nevents. A python implementation is provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 7 Aug 2022 19:49:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2023 23:20:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-09"}
