e achieved a simultaneous description of\nboth charged hadron, D meson, and inclusive jet observables. To further extract\nthe transport coefficients, a Bayesian analysis is conducted which constrains\nthe parameters in the transport models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 18:13:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-01"}
