mass without additional adjustments. We\nfind that the dissipation by buoyancy waves constitutes a necessary and\nrelevant extension of the turbulent convection model in use.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 20:14:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-16"}
