unable, and it can be optimized proportional\nto the computational cost and accuracy. Finally, we sketch the idea of how the\nCLC can make the consistency near the atomistic-continuum interface by\neliminating ghost forces. The energy of a one-dimensional atomic chain with a\nfinite range of interaction is relaxed to validate the CLC method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 22:48:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
