y\nnever satisfied, except for a brief period %for a brief stage around $\\sim 0.2$\nMyr at the snowline for $\\alpha_{\\rm{t}}=10^{-5}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2022 03:06:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-07"}
