g a U.S. registry. Results\nshowed that years closer to the time of interest were better at predicting\nfuture incidence rates in the CF example.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2022 15:52:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
